Author: homoeconomicus2017
Text: yes! for sure. when ~ in popular culture ~ people talk about trigger warnings—this is why. you’re literally being triggered in the way that non-ED people talk about being triggered. it’s definitely common and it used to happen to be.

Author: LowCalPal
Text: Sounds like [depersonalization](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Depersonalization), which is common in EDs.
